# Development Standards

## Core Web Vitals

- **LCP** (Largest Contentful Paint): Target < 2.5s
- **CLS** (Cumulative Layout Shift): Target < 0.1
- **INP** (Interactions to Next Paint): Target < 200ms for responsiveness

## Images

- Use WebP format (convert via `tools/png_to_webp.py`)
- Specify width and height on all images
- Use `loading="lazy"` for below-fold; `loading="eager"` for above-fold
- Descriptive alt text for all images

## Links

- Use `rel="noopener noreferrer"` for external links with `target="_blank"`

## Resource Hints

- `preconnect` for critical third-party domains (e.g., analytics)
- `dns-prefetch` for optional third parties

## Error Handling

- Wrap async code in try-catch
- Use descriptive error logging
- Provide fallbacks where appropriate
